 a commandment I give unto them, that they shall not ",["boast",["study-note-ref","a",[["Prov. 4:24","ot/prov/4.24"],"; ",["Rom. 3:27","nt/rom/3.27"],"; ",["D&C 105:24","dc-testament/dc/105.24"],". ",["TG Boast","tg/boast"],"."]]]," themselves of these things, neither speak them before the world; for these things are given unto you for your profit and for salvation."]],[74,["Verily, verily, I say unto you, they who believe not on your words, and are not ",["baptized",["study-note-ref","a",[["2 Ne. 9:23","bofm/2-ne/9.23"],"; ",["D&C 76:52 (50–52)","dc-testament/dc/76.52"],"; ",["137:6","dc-testament/dc/137.6"],". ",["TG Baptism, Essential","tg/baptism-essential"],"."]]]," in water in my name, for the ",["remission",["study-note-ref","b",[["TG Remission of Sins","tg/remission-of-sins"],"."]]]," of their sins, that they may receive the Holy Ghost, shall be ",["damned",["study-note-ref","c",[["John 3:18","nt/john/3.18"],"; ",["12:48","nt/john/12.48"],"."]]],", and shall not come into my Father’s kingdom where my Father and I am."]],[75,["And this revelation unto you, and commandment, is in force from this very hour upon all the ",["world",["study-note-ref","a",[["TG Missionary Work","tg/missionary-work"],"; ",["Revelation","tg/revelation"],"; ",["World","tg/world"],"."]]],", and the gospel is unto all who have not received it."]],[76,["But, verily I say unto all those to whom the kingdom has been given—from you it ",["must",["study-note-ref","a",[["Isa. 49:6 (5–7)","ot/isa/49.6"],"."]]]," be ",["preached",["study-note-ref","b",[["TG Priesthood, Magnifying Callings within","tg/priesthood-magnifying-callings-within"],"."]]]," unto them, that they shall repent of their former evil works; for they are to be upbraided for their evil ",["hearts",["study-note-ref","c",[["TG Hardheartedness","tg/hardheartedness"],"."]]]," of unbelief, and your brethren in Zion for their ",["rebellion",["study-note-ref","d",["IE in April 1832."]]]," against you at the time I sent you."]],[77,["And again I say unto you, my friends, for from henceforth I shall call you ",["friends",["study-note-ref","a",[["D&C 84:63","dc-testament/dc/84.63"],". ",["TG Friendship","tg/friendship"],"."]]],", it is expedient that I give unto you this commandment, that ye become even as my friends in days when I was with them, traveling to preach the gospel in my power;"]],[78,["For I suffered them not to have ",["purse",["study-note-ref","a",[["Matt. 10:9 (9–10)","nt/matt/10.9"],"; ",["Luke 10:4","nt/luke/10.4"],"; ",["22:35 (35–36)","nt/luke/22.35"],"; ",["D&C 24:18","dc-testament/dc/24.18"],"."]]]," or scrip, neither two coats."]],[79,["Behold, I ",["send",["study-note-ref","a",[["TG Delegation of Responsibility","tg/delegation-of-responsibility"],"."]]]," you out to ",["prove",["study-note-ref","b",[["TG Test","tg/test"],"."]]]," the world, and the laborer is worthy of his ",["hire",["study-note-ref","c",[["D&C 31:5","dc-testament/dc/31.5"],"."]]],"."]],[80,["And any man that shall go and preach this ",["gospel",["study-note-ref","a",[["Matt. 9:35","nt/matt/9.35"],"; ",["JS—M 1:31","pgp/js-m/1.31"],"."]]]," of the kingdom, and fail not to continue ",["faithful",["study-note-ref","b",[["TG Dependability","tg/dependability"],"."]]]," in all things, shall not be weary in ",["",159],"mind, neither darkened, neither in body, limb, nor joint; and a ",["hair",["study-note-ref","c",[["Luke 21:18","nt/luke/21.18"],"."]]]," of his head shall not fall to the ground unnoticed. And they shall not go hungry, neither athirst."]],[81,["Therefore, take ye no ",["thought",["study-note-ref","a",[["Matt. 6:25","nt/matt/6.25"],"; ",["Luke 12:22","nt/luke/12.22"],"."]]]," for the morrow, for what ye shall eat, or what ye shall drink, or wherewithal ye shall be clothed."]],[82,["For, ",["consider",["study-note-ref","a",[["Matt. 6:28","nt/matt/6.28"],"."]]]," the ",["lilies",["study-note-ref","b",[["TG Nature, Earth","tg/nature-earth"],"."]]]," of the field, how they grow, they toil not, neither do they spin; and the kingdoms of the world, in all their glory, are not arrayed like one of these."]],[83,["For your ",["Father",["study-note-ref","a",[["TG Man, a Spirit Child of Heavenly Father","tg/man-a-spirit-child-of-heavenly-father"],"."]]],", who is in heaven, ",["knoweth",["study-note-ref","b",[["Matt. 6:8, 32","nt/matt/6.8,32"],"."]]]," that you have need of all these things."]],[84,["Therefore, let the morrow take ",["thought",["study-note-ref","a",[["Matt. 6:34","nt/matt/6.34"],"."]]]," for the things of itself."]],[85,["Neither take ye thought beforehand ",["what",["study-note-ref","a",[["Matt. 10:19 (19–20)","nt/matt/10.19"],"; ",["Luke 12:11 (11–12)","nt/luke/12.11"],"; ",["21:14","nt/luke/21.14"],"; ",["D&C 100:6","dc-testament/dc/100.6"],"."]]]," ye shall say; but ",["treasure",["study-note-ref","b",[["Alma 17:2 (2–3)","bofm/alma/17.2"],"; ",["Hel. 5:18 (18–19)","bofm/hel/5.18"],"; ",["D&C 6:20","dc-testament/dc/6.20"],"; ",["11:26 (21–26)","dc-testament/dc/11.26"],"; ",["24:6","dc-testament/dc/24.6"],"; ",["100:5 (5–8)","dc-testament/dc/100.5"],". ",["TG Meditation","tg/meditation"],"; ",["Mind","tg/mind"],"; ",["Motivations","tg/motivations"],"; ",["Study","tg/study"],"."]]]," up in your minds continually the words of life, and it shall be ",["given",["study-note-ref","c",[["TG Teaching with the Spirit","tg/teaching-with-the-spirit"],"."]]]," you in the very hour that portion that shall be meted unto every man."]],[86,["Therefore, let no man among you, for this commandment is unto all the ",["faithful",["study-note-ref","a",[["Matt. 24:45","nt/matt/24.45"],"; ",["D&C 58:26 (26–29)","dc-testament/dc/58.26"],"; ",["107:100 (99–100)","dc-testament/dc/107.100"],"."]]]," who are called of God in the church unto the ministry, from this hour take purse or scrip, that goeth forth to proclaim this gospel of the kingdom."]],[87,["Behold, I send you out to ",["reprove",["study-note-ref","a",[["TG Missionary Work","tg/missionary-work"],"."]]]," the world of all their unrighteous deeds, and to teach them of a judgment which is to come."]],[88,["And whoso ",["receiveth",["study-note-ref","a",[["Matt. 10:40 (40–42)","nt/matt/10.40"],"; ",["John 13:20","nt/john/13.20"],"; ",["3 Jn. 1:5 (1–14)","nt/3-jn/1.5"],"."]]]," you, there I will be also, for I will go ",["before",["study-note-ref","b",[["Ex. 23:23","ot/ex/23.23"],"; ",["Lev. 26:12 (3–13)","ot/lev/26.12"],"; ",["Judg. 4:14","ot/judg/4.14"],"; ",["Ether 1:42 (42–43)","bofm/ether/1.42"],"."]]]," your face. I will be on your right hand and on your left, and my ",["Spirit",["study-note-ref","c",[["TG God, Spirit of","tg/god-spirit-of"],"."]]]," shall be in your hearts, and mine ",["angels",["study-note-ref","d",[["D&C 84:42","dc-testament/dc/84.42"],". ",["TG Angels","tg/angels"],"."]]]," round about you, to bear you up."]],[89,["Whoso receiveth you receiveth me; and the same will feed you, and clothe you, and give you money."]],[90,["And he who feeds you, or clothes you, or gives you money, shall in nowise ",["lose",["study-note-ref","a",[["Matt. 10:42","nt/matt/10.42"],"; ",["Mark 9:41","nt/mark/9.41"],"."]]]," his reward."]],[91,["And he that doeth not these things is not my disciple; by this you may know ",["my disciples",["study-note-ref","a",[["John 13:35","nt/john/13.35"],"."]]],"."]],[92,["He that receiveth you not, go away from him alone by yourselves, and ",["cleanse",["study-note-ref","a",[["Matt. 10:14","nt/matt/10.14"],"; ",["Luke 9:5","nt/luke/9.5"],"; ",["D&C 60:15","dc-testament/dc/60.15"],". ",["TG Wash","tg/wash"],"."]]]," your feet even with water, pure water, whether in heat or in cold, and bear testimony of it unto your Father which is in heaven, and return not again unto that man."]],[93,["And in whatsoever village or city ye enter, do likewise."]],[94,["Nevertheless, search diligently and spare not; and wo unto that house, or that village or city that rejecteth you, or your words, or your testimony concerning me."]],[95,["Wo, I say again, unto that house, or that village or city that rejecteth you, or your words, or your testimony of me;"]],[96,["For I, the ",["Almighty",["study-note-ref","a",[["TG God, Power of","tg/god-power-of"],"."]]],", have laid my hands upon the nations, to ",["scourge",["study-note-ref","b",[["D&C 1:14 (13–14)","dc-testament/dc/1.14"],"."]]]," them for their ",["wickedness",["study-note-ref","c",[["TG Wickedness","tg/wickedness"],"."]]],"."]],[97,["And ",["plagues",["study-note-ref","a",[["TG Plague","tg/plague"],"."]]]," shall go forth, and they shall not be taken from the earth until I have completed my work, which shall be cut ",["short",["study-note-ref","b",[["Matt. 24:22","nt/matt/24.22"],"."]]]," in righteousness—"]],[98,["Until all shall ",["know",["study-note-ref","a",[["TG God, Knowledge about","tg/god-knowledge-about"],"."]]]," me, who remain, even from the least unto the greatest, and shall be filled with ",["",160],"the knowledge of the Lord, and shall ",["see",["study-note-ref","b",[["Isa. 52:8","ot/isa/52.8"],"."]]]," eye to eye, and shall lift up their voice, and with the voice together ",["sing",["study-note-ref","c",[["Ps. 96:1","ot/ps/96.1"],"; ",["Rev. 15:3","nt/rev/15.3"],"; ",["D&C 25:12","dc-testament/dc/25.12"],"; ",["133:56","dc-testament/dc/133.56"],". ",["TG Singing","tg/singing"],"."]]]," this new song, saying:"]],[99,[["The Lord hath brought again Zion;",["line"]],["The Lord hath ",["redeemed",["study-note-ref","a",[["Deut. 21:8","ot/deut/21.8"],"; ",["Ps. 25:22","ot/ps/25.22"],"; ",["Rom. 11:26 (25–28)","nt/rom/11.26"],"; ",["D&C 43:29","dc-testament/dc/43.29"],"; ",["100:13","dc-testament/dc/100.13"],"; ",["136:18","dc-testament/dc/136.18"],"."]]]," his people, ",["Israel",["study-note-ref","b",[["TG Israel, Restoration of","tg/israel-restoration-of"],"."]]],",",["line"]],["According to the ",["election",["study-note-ref","c",[["TG Election","tg/election"],"."]]]," of ",["grace",["study-note-ref","d",[["TG Grace","tg/grace"],"."]]],",",["line"]],["Which was brought to pass by the faith",["line"]],["And ",["covenant",["study-note-ref","e",[["TG Abrahamic Covenant","tg/abrahamic-covenant"],"."]]]," of their fathers.",["line"]]]],[100,[["The Lord hath redeemed his people;",["line"]],["And Satan is ",["bound",["study-note-ref","a",[["Rev. 20:2 (2–3)","nt/rev/20.2"],"; ",["D&C 43:31","dc-testament/dc/43.31"],"; ",["45:55","dc-testament/dc/45.55"],"; ",["88:110","dc-testament/dc/88.110"],"; ",["101:28","dc-testament/dc/101.28"],"."]]]," and ",["time",["study-note-ref","b",[["Alma 40:8","bofm/alma/40.8"],". ",["TG Time","tg/time"],"."]]]," is no longer.",["line"]],["The Lord hath gathered all things in ",["one",["study-note-ref","c",[["Eph. 1:10","nt/eph/1.10"],"; ",["D&C 27:13","dc-testament/dc/27.13"],"."]]],".",["line"]],["The Lord hath brought down ",["Zion",["study-note-ref","d",[["D&C 45:12 (11–14)","dc-testament/dc/45.12"],"; ",["Moses 7:63 (62–64)","pgp/moses/7.63"],". ",["TG Zion","tg/zion"],"."]]]," from above.",["line"]],["The Lord hath ",["brought up",["study-note-ref","e",[["D&C 76:102","dc-testament/dc/76.102"],"; ",["88:96","dc-testament/dc/88.96"],"."]]]," Zion from beneath.",["line"]]]],[101,[["The ",["earth",["study-note-ref","a",[["TG Earth, Destiny of","tg/earth-destiny-of"],"."]]]," hath travailed and ",["brought forth",["study-note-ref","b",[["Moses 7:64 (54–67)","pgp/moses/7.64"],"."]]]," her strength;",["line"]],["And truth is established in her bowels;",["line"]],["And the heavens have smiled upon her;",["line"]],["And she is clothed with the ",["glory",["study-note-ref","c",[["TG Glory","tg/glory"],"."]]]," of her God;",["line"]],["For he ",["stands",["study-note-ref","d",[["TG God, Presence of","tg/god-presence-of"],"."]]]," in the midst of his ",["people",["study-note-ref","e",[["Jer. 30:22","ot/jer/30.22"],"."]]],".",["line"]]]],[102,[["Glory, and honor, and power, and might,",["line"]],["Be ascribed to our God; for he is full of ",["mercy",["study-note-ref","a",[["TG God, Mercy of","tg/god-mercy-of"],"."]]],",",["line"]],["Justice, grace and truth, and ",["peace",["study-note-ref","b",[["TG Peace of God","tg/peace-of-god"],"."]]],",",["line"]],["Forever and ever, Amen.",["line"]]]],[103,["And again, verily, verily, I say unto you, it is expedient that every man who goes forth to proclaim mine everlasting gospel, that inasmuch as they have ",["families",["study-note-ref","a",[["TG Family","tg/family"],"."]]],", and receive ",["money",["study-note-ref","b",[["TG Family, Managing Finances in","tg/family-managing-finances-in"],"."]]]," by gift, that they should send it unto them or make use of it for their benefit, as the Lord shall direct them, for thus it seemeth me good."]],[104,["And let all those who have not families, who receive ",["money",["study-note-ref","a",[["D&C 51:8 (8–13)","dc-testament/dc/51.8"],"; ",["58:51 (49–51)","dc-testament/dc/58.51"],"."]]],", send it up unto the bishop in Zion, or unto the bishop in Ohio, that it may be consecrated for the bringing forth of the revelations and the printing thereof, and for establishing Zion."]],[105,["And if any man shall give unto any of you a coat, or a suit, take the old and cast it unto the ",["poor",["study-note-ref","a",[["TG Poor","tg/poor"],"."]]],", and go on your way rejoicing."]],[106,["And if any man among you be ",["strong",["study-note-ref","a",[["TG Fellowshipping","tg/fellowshipping"],"."]]]," in the Spirit, let him take with him him that is ",["weak",["study-note-ref","b",[["Rom. 14:1 (1–4, 10, 13)","nt/rom/14.1"],"."]]],", that he may be ",["edified",["study-note-ref","c",[["TG Edification","tg/edification"],"."]]]," in all ",["meekness",["study-note-ref","d",[["TG Meek","tg/meek"],"."]]],", that he may become strong also."]],[107,["Therefore, take with you those who are ordained unto the ",["lesser priesthood",["study-note-ref","a",[["TG Priesthood, Aaronic","tg/priesthood-aaronic"],"."]]],", and send them ",["before",["study-note-ref","b",[["Luke 10:1 (1–12)","nt/luke/10.1"],"."]]]," you to make appointments, and to prepare the way, and to fill appointments that you yourselves are not able to fill."]],[108,["Behold, this is the way that mine apostles, in ancient days, built up my church unto me."]],[109,["Therefore, let every man stand in his own ",["office",["study-note-ref","a",[["TG Church Organization","tg/church-organization"],"."]]],", and ",["labor",["study-note-ref","b",[["TG Priesthood, Magnifying Callings within","tg/priesthood-magnifying-callings-within"],"."]]]," in his own calling; and let not the ",["head",["study-note-ref","c",[["1 Cor. 12:21","nt/1-cor/12.21"],"."]]]," say unto the feet it hath no need of the feet; for without the feet how shall the body be able to stand?"]],[110,["Also the body hath need of every ",["member",["study-note-ref","a",[["TG Church","tg/church"],"."]]],", that all may be ",["edified",["study-note-ref","b",[["TG Edification","tg/edification"],"."]]]," together, that the system may be kept perfect."]],[111,["And behold, the ",["high priests",["study-note-ref","a",[["TG High Priest, Melchizedek Priesthood","tg/high-priest-melchizedek-priesthood"],"."]]]," should travel, and also the elders, and also the lesser ",["priests",["study-note-ref","b",[["TG Priest, Aaronic Priesthood","tg/priest-aaronic-priesthood"],"."]]],"; but the ",["deacons",["study-note-ref","c",[["TG Deacon","tg/deacon"],"."]]]," and ",["teachers",["study-note-ref","d",[["TG Teacher","tg/teacher"],"."]]]," should be appointed to ",["watch",["study-note-ref","e",[["TG Watch","tg/watch"],"."]]]," over the church, to be standing ministers unto the church."]],[112,["And the bishop, Newel K. Whitney, also should travel round about and among all the churches, searching after the poor to ",["administer",["study-note-ref","a",[["TG Poor","tg/poor"],"; ",["Welfare","tg/welfare"],"."]]]," to their wants by ",["humbling",["study-note-ref","b",[["D&C 56:16","dc-testament/dc/56.16"],"."]]]," the rich and the proud."]],[113,["He should also employ an ",["agent",["study-note-ref","a",[["D&C 51:8 (8–12)","dc-testament/dc/51.8"],"; ",["53:4","dc-testament/dc/53.4"],"; ",["90:22","dc-testament/dc/90.22"],"."]]]," to take charge and to do his secular business as he shall direct."]],[114,["Nevertheless, let the bishop go unto the city of New York, also to the city of Albany, and also to the city of Boston, and warn the people of those ",["cities",["study-note-ref","a",[["Matt. 11:20","nt/matt/11.20"],"; ",["Alma 34:31 (31–36)","bofm/alma/34.31"],"; ",["3 Ne. 9:3","bofm/3-ne/9.3"],"."]]]," with the sound of the gospel, with a loud voice, of the ",["desolation",["study-note-ref","b",[["D&C 1:13 (13–14)","dc-testament/dc/1.13"],"."]]]," and utter abolishment which await them if they do reject these things."]],[115,["For if they do reject these things the hour of their judgment is nigh, and their house shall be left unto them ",["desolate",["study-note-ref","a",[["Luke 13:35","nt/luke/13.35"],"."]]],"."]],[116,["Let him ",["trust",["study-note-ref","a",[["Prov. 28:25 (25–26)","ot/prov/28.25"],"; ",["Isa. 50:10","ot/isa/50.10"],"; ",["D&C 11:12","dc-testament/dc/11.12"],". ",["TG Trust in God","tg/trust-in-god"],"."]]]," in me and he shall not be ",["confounded",["study-note-ref","b",[["Ps. 22:5","ot/ps/22.5"],"; ",["1 Pet. 2:6","nt/1-pet/2.6"],"; ",["D&C 49:27","dc-testament/dc/49.27"],"."]]],"; and a ",["hair",["study-note-ref","c",[["Matt. 10:30","nt/matt/10.30"],"; ",["Luke 21:18","nt/luke/21.18"],"."]]]," of his head shall not fall to the ground unnoticed."]],[117,["And verily I say unto you, the rest of my servants, go ye forth as your circumstances shall permit, in your several callings, unto the great and notable cities and villages, ",["reproving",["study-note-ref","a",[["Titus 1:13","nt/titus/1.13"],"."]]]," the world in righteousness of all their unrighteous and ungodly deeds, setting forth clearly and understandingly the desolation of ",["abomination",["study-note-ref","b",[["TG Abomination of Desolation","tg/abomination-of-desolation"],"; ",["Warn","tg/warn"],"."]]]," in the last days."]],[118,["For, with you saith the Lord ",["Almighty",["study-note-ref","a",[["TG God, Power of","tg/god-power-of"],"."]]],", I will ",["rend",["study-note-ref","b",[["Dan. 2:44 (34–35, 44–45)","ot/dan/2.44"],"."]]]," their ",["kingdoms",["study-note-ref","c",[["TG Kings, Earthly","tg/kings-earthly"],"."]]],"; I will not only ",["shake",["study-note-ref","d",[["Joel 2:10","ot/joel/2.10"],"; ",["D&C 43:18","dc-testament/dc/43.18"],"; ",["45:33 (33, 48)","dc-testament/dc/45.33"],"; ",["88:87 (87, 90)","dc-testament/dc/88.87"],". ",["TG Last Days","tg/last-days"],"."]]]," the earth, but the ",["starry",["study-note-ref","e",[["D&C 21:6","dc-testament/dc/21.6"],"."]]]," heavens shall tremble."]],[119,["For I, the Lord, have put forth my hand to exert the ",["powers",["study-note-ref","a",[["Matt. 24:29","nt/matt/24.29"],"."]]]," of heaven; ye cannot see it now, yet a ",["little while",["study-note-ref","b",[["Heb. 10:37","nt/heb/10.37"],"."]]]," and ye shall see it, and know that I am, and that ",["I",["study-note-ref","c",[["Ex. 15:18","ot/ex/15.18"],"."]]]," will ",["come",["study-note-ref","d",[["D&C 1:36 (12, 35–36)","dc-testament/dc/1.36"],"; ",["29:11 (9–11)","dc-testament/dc/29.11"],"; ",["45:59","dc-testament/dc/45.59"],"; ",["104:59","dc-testament/dc/104.59"],". ",["TG Jesus Christ, Millennial Reign","tg/jesus-christ-millennial-reign"],"; ",["Jesus Christ, Second Coming","tg/jesus-christ-second-coming"],"."]]]," and reign with my people."]],[120,["I am ",["Alpha and Omega",["study-note-ref","a",[["D&C 35:1","dc-testament/dc/35.1"],"."]]],", the beginning and the end. Amen."]]],"volume":"dc-testament"}